PLAIN
DAY_LIGHT
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
A large, iron bridge spans the Eltinmar River at this point. The bridge is very old, pre-dating the Cataclysm, and shows the signs of its age. The beams and girders have turned to an orange hue from the rust that covers them. Loose beams swing precariously in the wind and water sprays through large holes in the bridge's surface. The overgrown road leading east seems to offer more safety.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT E 554
EXIT ABOVE 2150
ITEM 0 61 ADJ1=272 ADJ2=169
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 0
Though the bridge is in deplorable condition, it seems as if a wary climber could make his way across. Any slip however, and one might plummet into the icy-blue waters below.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFVERB GO 0
	ECHO PLAYER You'll have to climb that.
	CLEARVERB
ENDIF
IFVERB CLIMB 0
	SKILLCHECK 5 0 DUMMY4
	IFVAR DUMMY4 >= 80
		ECHO PLAYER You swiftly cross the bridge. It wasn't as bad as it looked.
		ECHO OTHERS %N crosses the bridge unexpectantly fast.
		MOVE 557
		AFFECT 557
		IFVAR RAC ! 8
			ECHO OTHERS %N steps off the bridge looking pleased with %iself.
		ENDIF
		IFVAR RAC = 8
			ECHO OTHERS %N arrives.
		ENDIF
		AFFECT 555
	ENDIF
	IFVAR DUMMY4 < 80
		IFVAR DUMMY4 >= 40
		ECHO PLAYER You carefully pick your way across the bridge.
		ECHO OTHERS %N carefully picks %h way across the bridge.
		MOVE 557
		AFFECT 557
		ECHO OTHERS %N gingerly steps off the bridge.
		AFFECT 555
		ENDIF
	ENDIF
	IFVAR DUMMY4 < 40
		IFVAR DUMMY4 >= 0
		ECHO PLAYER A third of the way over, you trip and fall, but are able to grab a hold of a rail to catch yourself and continue.
		ECHO OTHERS You see %n nearly fall, but then recover to complete the trip.
		MOVE 557
		AFFECT 557
		ECHO OTHERS %N gets off the bridge in a hurry.
		AFFECT 555
		ENDIF
	ENDIF
	IFVAR DUMMY4 < 0
		ECHO OTHERS %N has fallen in the water and is being carried away by the current!
		ECHO PLAYER You trip and fall from the bridge into the water.%c%cYou struggle to the surface coughing and sputtering.%c%cYou are being swept away!
		AFFECT 2014
		ECHO OTHERS %N just fell from the Eltinmar Bridge into the river!
		AFFECT 555
		MOVE 2014
	ENDIF
	CLEARVERB
ENDIF
