	ECHO OTHERS %n climbs up to the ledge from the face below.
	AFFECT 743
   ENDIF
   IFVAR abclimbroll < 70
      ECHO PLAYER You suffer an attack of acute anxiety and abort the climb.
      ECHO OTHERS %n starts to climb up the crevice, but cannot.
   ENDIF
   IFVAR abclimbroll > 69
      IFVAR abclimbroll < 131
         ECHO PLAYER You start up the crevice with care, but slip and fall.
         ECHO OTHERS %n starts up the crevice with care, but slips and falls.
         DAMAGE CRUSH 30 A dull thud sounds as ground and body meet.
         POSITION LAY
         RANDOM DUMMY1 1 100 0
         ADD DUMMY1 AGI
         IFVAR DUMMY1 < 170
            ECHO PLAYER You cannot seem to hold on to the ledge...
            ECHO OTHERS %n bounces off the ledge and down the mountain.
            MOVE 742
            AFFECT 742
            ECHO OTHERS %n plummets from the ledge above.
            DAMAGE CRUSH 20 Rock is most unyielding to falling bodies...
            RANDOM DUMMY2 1 100 0
            ADD DUMMY2 AGI
            IFVAR DUMMY2 < 150
               ECHO PLAYER Your momentum carries you on down the slope.
               ECHO OTHERS %n continues to fall on down the slope.
               MOVE 736
               AFFECT 736
               ECHO OTHERS %n comes tumbling down the slope from above.
               DAMAGE CRUSH 10 A solid rock finally stops the fall.
            ELSE
               ECHO PLAYER You manage to check your speed and stop.
               ECHO OTHERS %n manages to check %h speed and stop.
            ENDIF
         ELSE
            ECHO PLAYER You manage to grab the ledge and stop.
            ECHO OTHERS %n manages to grab the ledge and stop.
         ENDIF
      ENDIF
   ENDIF
ENDIF
