NUMBER 1901
NAME Earthen cave
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
You are in a rocky cave with a packed earth floor. The ceiling arcs high
enough over your head that you do not need to stoop to avoid braining
yourself on rocky outcroppings. The lack of light makes the cave very
dark, but the earthen floor is relatively smooth, so you don't need to
worry about tripping over anything. The rich scent of damp earth fills
your nose. There is a hole in the ceiling.
*DESCRIPTION_END
